description.en-us: Super Rigs is the sixth series of transport trucks and included bonus vehicles, coming after Long Haulers , Pavement Pounders , Truckin' Transporters , Racing Rigs , and Trackin' Trucks . The series started in 2014 and received a logo in 2020.
